title: The server Transfer is not working
body:
iv'e been trying to transfer my account from EUW to EUNE 

Whenever i do it , it tells i have to wait 2 min , then i get a messagebox that the Transfer is completed .. 

then the launcher restart. and i cant login on EUNE because my account is still on EUW *WITHOUT LOSING RP*

Many other players are having the same problem

replies.body: That's strange!  I looked into this for you and do see that the transfer wasn't able to process.  Hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and our account team can look into this with you directly.  See you there!

Can you try transfereing an account from EUW to EUNE yourslef ?
to check if the problem is not general because im not the only one.
This is something best handled by our account team, who have the resources to  investigate and look for any quirks during the transfer process.
